# UI component library — @tahti/ui

**Single source of truth:** `packages/ui` (`@tahti/ui`). Every visual component, layout shell, and shared UI utility lives there.

## Rules for agents

1. **Import UI from `@tahti/ui`** (or `@/components/ui`, which re-exports the package — no new implementations in `apps/web`).
2. **Never add** Button, Panel, Field, layout shells, or brand chrome under `apps/web/src/components/ui/` or parallel folders. Add to `packages/ui` and export from `packages/ui/src/index.ts`.
3. **Never use inline `style={{…}}` for colors, borders, or typography** when a `@tahti/ui` class or component exists. Use design tokens (`var(--cyan)`, `var(--tahti-primary)`) via CSS in `packages/ui/src/styles/`.
4. **Read `docs/design/README.md`** before writing or changing UI.

## Surfaces and CSS (import once per route layout)

| Surface | Routes | CSS imports |
|---------|--------|-------------|
| **Brand (dark)** | `/c`, `/u`, `/r`, marketing | `tokens.css`, `components.css`, `styles/brand-channel.css` |
| **Studio (dark dashboard)** | `/dashboard` | `tokens.css`, `components.css`, `styles/brand-studio.css` |
| **Admin (forms in mixed pages)** | root `globals.css` | `styles/admin-tokens.css`, `styles/admin-ui.css` |
| **Auth / gateway (light)** | `/login`, `/join`, `/`, `/help` | `styles/brand-public.css` + admin tokens as needed |
| **Embed (dark minimal)** | `/embed` | `styles/embed.css` |

## Component map

| Need | Import from `@tahti/ui` |
|------|-------------------------|
| Forms, panels, dashboard | `Button`, `Panel`, `Field`, `Input`, `Heading`, `Text`, … |
| Channel page | `ChannelPageLayout`, `ChannelHeader` |
| Artist profile / subscribe | `ProfilePageLayout`, `ProfileHero` |
| Smart link | `SmartLinkPageLayout` |
| Dashboard shell | `StudioShell`, `StudioSidebar`, `StudioTopNav` |
| Live badge, stats | `LiveBadge`, `Stat`, `StatGrid`, `Callout` |
| Marketing site | `MarketingButton`, `Nav`, `Card`, `SectionHeader` |
| Escaped user text | `SafePlainText` |
| Auth wordmark | `BrandLogo` |
| Iframe embeds | `EmbedShell` + `styles/embed.css` |

## Adding a new component

1. Implement in `packages/ui/src/admin/`, `brand/`, or `marketing/` (match surface).
2. Add styles to the matching file under `packages/ui/src/styles/`.
3. Export from the folder `index.ts` and `packages/ui/src/index.ts`.
4. Run `pnpm lint` and `pnpm format:check`.

## Anti-patterns

- Duplicating `packages/ui` under `apps/web/src/components/ui/*.tsx`
- Light-theme hex (`#eee`, `#111`) on brand routes
- Raw `<button style={{ background: '#16a34a' }}>` instead of `.tier-subscribe-btn` or `Button`
